&lt;p&gt;This is a fixed term post to 31 March 2022 due to funding.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are a Hywel Dda Health Board employee this post will only be offered on a secondment basis and you will need to have gained your line managers approval for the secondment prior to going to interview.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We are looking to recruit a highly skilled, enthusiastic and motivated individual to fill the role of Senior Project Manager (2 posts available).&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The postholder will be responsible for managing and controlling the delivery of complex Digital projects which form part of the Digital Programme and key to the successful implementation of the Health Board&#39;s Strategy.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The successful applicant will work closely with our Clinical, ICT, Programme &amp; Systems and Information teams to manage the implementation of the Digital project objectives, contributing to organisational innovation and delivering high quality patient care. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Applicants should be educated to Masters level and possess management qualification or equivalent experience. They will also have extensive experience of working in a senior project management role and experience of achieving ambitious targets and implementing ICT solutions. Applicants should possess PRINCE2 Practitioner or equivalent professional project management qualification. Applications should have excellent communication, negotiation, persuasion and influencing skills and be a strong project manager.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Exposure to ITIL based Service Management transition and Maturity Models would also be beneficial.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; English and/or Welsh speakers are equally welcome to apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Interviews will be held on 25th November 2020.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameRichard SmartJob titleHead of Clinical Systems and Informatics ProjectsEmail addressRichard.Smart@wales.nhs.ukTelephone number01970 635301&lt;/p&gt;
